binary semaphore (semaphore is a flag)
Flag up when 1 goroutine is writing to variable
Put flag up, use shared variable, put flag down.
1st call to Lock() puts the flag up
2nd call to Lock() will block the calling goroutine... it has to wait.
when Unlock() is called, the next goroutine will continue
So... call Lock() then Unlock() to use shared variables.
